☃️ v0.2 Release Roadmap
-------------------------

I'm not really sure whene v0.2 is going to be released, because v0.1 really hasn't been officially launched yet. I used the snowman emoji because I thought Winter, but we're probably talking February 24 and not December 24. I'm looking to get some big features into v0.2, including auto-differentiation, GPGPU programming, and better distributed program support.